modName: Ancient Nord Helmet - Female Khajiit - Fix
summary: Quick and dirty edit to fix the clipping present in the default mesh for the Female Khajiit.
descriptionHtml:
Just a quick and dirty edit with NifScope to decrease/remove the clipping that occurs with the vanilla Ancient Nord Helmet on the female Khajiit.

It does make the helmet slightly longer, but this is not really noticeable and I\'d prefer a bit longer helmet to clipping.

*This does not change any other version of the helmet as the female khajiit has her own version of the helmet
author: ErikRedbeard
